ook.com/450867315005279/posts/2299277576830901/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F450867315005279%2Fposts%2F2299277576830901%2F&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=82846e4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/450867315005279/posts/2299277576830901/</a><br />\n<br />\n612嗰日一位16歲女學生嘅心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUxq7VC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUxq7VC.gif&h=721ac9a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少年於金鐘一帶背向警察站立，遭十多名速龍小隊成員<span style=\"color: red;\">強行拉扯到地上用警棍圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQu85Ja.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQu85Ja.gif&h=0ec58946&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名少女下午於立法會地下門外落單，遭近十名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">以盾牌及警棍按倒地上瘋狂圍毆</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wk41Gxi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwk41Gxi.gif&h=5c8616cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名手無寸鐵市民於大會堂對出方向，遭4-5名警員<span style=\"color: red;\">揮棍不停攻擊頭部倒地。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/4g17BRj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4g17BRj.gif&h=509faf8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名外藉男子於愛丁堡廣場附近，因行動不便獨自坐於花槽旁，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員以胡椒噴劑近距離向臉部射擊。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLz5ovx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLz5ovx.gif&h=58851dc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8PQzCe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8PQzCe.gif&h=58a9a71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvSnqJW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvSnqJW.gif&h=c1469b1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>下午時份於金鐘天橋附近一帶，一名中年婦人向警員哭求停止對香港人使用武力，<span style=\"color: red;\">遭警員近距離以不明武器擊中頭部。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/d6KQzNf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6KQzNf.gif&h=b3ebd9eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>一名市民於金鐘橋底下，遭警員<span style=\"color: red;\">瞄準頭部射擊</span>。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映：</span></span><br />\n示威者吐血<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhRCPds07zSM&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=582a65e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hRCPds07zSM</a> <br />\n<br />\n拖行暈倒示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGfhHJqNVPig&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=1ab85c50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GfhHJqNVPig</a> <br />\n<br />\n唔比救護車入<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmT8SH2EJctk&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=5c7954ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mT8SH2EJctk</a> <br />\n<br />\n地鐵站噴椒<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsQk9mLw07WM&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=27a60e24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sQk9mLw07WM</a> <br />\n<br />\n開槍<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9bbFANmVWZ4&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=3173bcc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9bbFANmVWZ4</a> <br />\n<br />\n向記者放tear gas<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcWZ0R67V5Yg&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAjbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=6a1a1ad7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cWZ0R67V5Yg</a> <br />\n<br />\n事後嚟張大合照慶功先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3BUJgDg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3BUJgDg.png&h=d811719e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9aef545d5250e6e9675c7011a7c001415256c15","tid":1217531,"uid":45551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:33:33.000Z","msg":"一哥 你會唔會對自己仔女 做同樣既事？"},{"pid":"8b9067adae880564e7a89ad588acfcf88ea1a9f9","tid":1217531,"uid":14600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9aef545d5250e6e9675c7011a7c001415256c15","tid":1217531,"uid":45551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:33:33.000Z","msg":"一哥 你會唔會對自己仔女 做同樣既事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我啲仔女唔係香港, Sor"},{"pid":"bc569b3d1529cd675ac1bb3ebb8b78e87a072e83","tid":1217531,"uid":85604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:35:07.000Z","msg":"學灘叔講:<br />\n阿sir我屌你老母自由閪係點解"},{"pid":"1a2468167163cf6cc3fee6271cde7add5649e28e","tid":1217531,"uid":109971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea345c3cd283fe7825096ee54f8645daf61faf06","tid":1217531,"uid":14600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f6f70bbd9210a58373967c83ec78b4bd47d8a7b","tid":1217531,"uid":109971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:22:03.000Z","msg":"點解對付完班學生同市民之後仲要去立法會影相<br />\n<br />\n記者朋友影到你地班手下仲要笑笑口，係唔係對付完市民之後好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁同當年菲律賓人質事件有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB